# Personal GitHub Token for API requests (starring, profile data)
# 
# For GitHub Actions:
# - Add PERSONAL_GITHUB_TOKEN as repository secret
# - Workflow will use this for user-scoped API calls
#
# For local development:
# Generate at: https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new
# - Use fine-grained token (recommended)
# - Set expiration (e.g., 90 days)  
# - Repository access: Public repositories only
# - Account permissions needed:
#   - Profile: Read
#   - Starring: Read
#
# Alternative classic token: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# - No scopes needed for public data access
PERSONAL_GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here